---

### **Tool/Function Registration**

Tools are registered via **`Microsoft.Extensions.AI.ChatOptions.Tools`** property:

```csharp
// Method 1: In ChatClientAgentOptions at creation time
var options = new ChatClientAgentOptions
{
    ChatOptions = new ChatOptions
    {
        Tools = new List<AITool>
        {
            AITool.FromMethod(
                typeof(MyTools).GetMethod("MyFunction"),
                "Function description"
            ),
            // ... more tools
        }
    }
};

// Method 2: Via ChatClientAgent constructor (first parameter variant)
var agent = new ChatClientAgent(
    chatClient,
    instructions: "You are a helpful assistant",
    name: "MyAgent",
    description: "Helps with tasks",
    tools: new List<AITool> { ... },  // Tools go here
    loggerFactory: loggerFactory,
    services: serviceProvider
);

// Method 3: Per-invocation via ChatClientAgentRunOptions
var runOptions = new ChatClientAgentRunOptions
{
    ChatOptions = new ChatOptions
    {
        Tools = new List<AITool> { ... }  // Runtime tools
    }
};
var response = await agent.RunAsync("message", session, runOptions);
```

